<span>Hello</span>    -- without enter 

static - source - public --> better to create css file in another folder with one of these names

1) <span style = "font-style : italic;">Hypertext Language</span> ---> go to CSS (каскадные таблицы стилей)
2) <span> Hypertexte Language </span> 
IN HEAD: 
<style> 
span {
font-style : italic
}
</style>
3) IN HTML :
<span> Hypertexte Language </span> 
<link rel = "stylesheet" href = "style.css">          -- connect css file
IN CSS:
span {
font-style : italic;
background-color: black;
color: white;
}

---------------------------------
To use different styles and etc. in TAG SPAN: 
<span></span>
<span class = "bold-text"></span>
GO TO CSS:
span{
font-style: italic;
}
.bold-text{
font-weight: bold;
}

-------------------------------------
TAG <a></a>
1) <a href = "" > HTML </a>                                       // if you dont want to add link -> write   href = "#" (заглушка)
2) <a href = "https://youtube.com" target = "_blank" > HTML </a>     // to open page in new window

